  - m_Id: 4173777387577344
    m_Localized: '> Progress:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4175611317641216
    m_Localized: Hello !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4175629659332608
    m_Localized: I have some items that you might need.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4178121440813056
    m_Localized: Shop
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4178186880344064
    m_Localized: End
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4179966552891392
    m_Localized: "Are you Richard\u2019s son?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4463865380134912
    m_Localized: Harvest Apples
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4464139041693696
    m_Localized: Go to the orchard and collect 5 fresh apples.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4466705087520768
    m_Localized: Can you help me harvest some apples?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4466719549480960
    m_Localized: You haven't got enough apples yet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4466739786997760
    m_Localized: Great job! These apples look delicious.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4467742053687296
    m_Localized: First Trip to the Farm
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4467756515647488
    m_Localized: Follow the Lawyer's advice and take the bus to the farm.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4467767789936640
    m_Localized: Take the bus at the station.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4467779437518848
    m_Localized: The farm is located quite far from town. Use the bus to get there;
      I will be waiting for you at the destination.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4468533573378048
    m_Localized: Welcome to the farm that your father, Richard, left behind.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4521209862479872
    m_Localized: For someone who has lived in the city as long as you have, I'm afraid
      you might have forgotten how to handle these farming tools, haven't you?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4523525449637888
    m_Localized: The Starting Kit
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4523555447300096
    m_Localized: Check the chest inside the house to collect the necessary items
      as instructed by the Lawyer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4523589777678336
    m_Localized: "Thu th\u1EADp d\u1EE5ng c\u1EE5 trong r\u01B0\u01A1ng"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4524209393819648
    m_Localized: Your father has left a few things for you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4524262640508928
    m_Localized: Please go inside and open the wooden chest in the corner. You'll
      find the necessary tools to begin your work here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4524305388855296
    m_Localized: Haven't you checked the chest yet? Everything you need is already
      sealed inside.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4524335927582720
    m_Localized: Very well. Now you have all the tools to legally take over this
      farm.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4535085714825216
    m_Localized: Farming Trial
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4535138982486016
    m_Localized: Receive wheat seeds from the Lawyer and plant them in the garden.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4535187971956736
    m_Localized: Plant wheat seeds
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4535253944164352
    m_Localized: I will give you some wheat seeds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4535273372180480
    m_Localized: Go out to the garden and plant these seeds there.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4535330448269312
    m_Localized: Haven't you planted the seeds yet? The garden is just outside, go
      get it done.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4535372085125120
    m_Localized: Very good. At this rate, the farm will be back in business soon.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4072872961040384
    m_Localized: Shadows of the Forest
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4072935170957312
    m_Localized: Please help me! My son wandered into the forest and hasn't returned.
      Please find him!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6238751828140032
    m_Localized: Have you found my son yet? Every second feels like an eternity...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6238816651108352
    m_Localized: So he went that way? Thank you... at least now I know he's still
      out there. Please, you have to bring him back!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6240082966011904
    m_Localized: Where could he have gone
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8181894685319168
    m_Localized: 'Resume '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
